1
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:34,940
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,009 --> 00:01:37,979
[Episode 16]

3
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:26,350
[Taiji Hall]

4
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,820
Your Highness,

5
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,890
these are all gifts
bestowed by His Majesty.

6
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,470
Just looking at them irritates me.

7
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,680
Her Highness doesn't like them.

8
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,540
Take them away.

9
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:52,750
Yes.

10
00:02:58,030 --> 00:03:00,090
How on earth did she manage to do that?

11
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,750
I told you long ago—

12
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,590
don't provoke Yu Wanyin.

13
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,660
But you just wouldn't listen.

14
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,750
Your Highness Consort Xie,

15
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,079
you dropped something.

16
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,590
This is a remedy

17
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,240
that His Highness Prince Duan found
for Your Highness.

18
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,350
Take it all at once.

19
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,680
It will take effect within four hours.

20
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,680
But Her Highness has already...

21
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,030
Ling.

22
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,270
Take it for me.

23
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,850
Eunuch, please deliver

24
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,640
a message to Prince Duan for me.

25
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,950
Please tell him to rest assured.

26
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,530
Then this servant will take his leave.

27
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,190
Your Highness,

28
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:54,470
why didn't you let me tell His Highness

29
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:56,400
that the matter has been resolved?

30
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,850
Physician Xiao risked his life to save me.

31
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,720
I don't want to drag him into this.

32
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,850
Give me that.

33
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,480
Dan,

34
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,660
today's Grand Longevity Banquet

35
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,190
is so lively

36
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,010
with songs and dances.

37
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:26,310
The Yan delegation you've been
thinking about has also come.

38
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,560
Are you satisfied?

39
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,790
Mother, you're thoughtful.

40
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,110
I was worried

41
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:34,159
that if we turned them away,

42
00:04:34,659 --> 00:04:36,260
it would only invite gossip.

43
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:37,750
And in the end,

44
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:41,050
it would hurt your reputation as well,
wouldn't it?

45
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,120
In that case,

46
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:48,430
I should thank you?

47
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,360
My son, you thought of everything.

48
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,090
Whether I'm thorough or not...

49
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,340
I still need to rely on my brother.

50
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:25,580
[Taiji Hall]

51
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,690
The Yan State delegation has arrived!

52
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,370
He's an expert fighter.

53
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,270
Really?

54
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:00,330
Mr. Bei,

55
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,800
I'm not really the focus
of tonight's banquet.

56
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,330
You should go watch over
His Majesty instead.

57
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:09,070
Who knows what unexpected things
might happen?

58
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:12,120
It's always good to have you
protecting him discreetly.

59
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,010
Mr. Bei, you...

60
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,600
Not even a token protest?

61
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,930
As expected, your mind isn't on me.

62
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,430
I am Haqina, Envoy of Yan!

63
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:30,070
We wish Your Majesty longevity

64
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,950
and the Empress Dowager good health!

65
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:36,770
May friendship between our two nations
last for generations!

66
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,600
You've come

67
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:47,960
from afar.

68
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,120
The journey

69
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,570
must have been tiring.

70
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

71
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:55,120
At our Emperor's instruction,

72
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:58,120
we've specially brought dancers
from our country

73
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,410
to perform for Your Majesty

74
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,200
as a token of our good wishes.

75
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,340
Excellent.

76
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,720
Please be seated.

77
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,230
Thank you, Your Majesty.

78
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,270
Yong'er.

79
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:21,840
Lady Yu?

80
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,940
Why did you arrive so late?

81
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,440
Forgive me, Lady Yu.

82
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,450
My...

83
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,520
stomach has been unsettled,

84
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,430
so I was delayed in my palace.

85
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:38,930
I haven't yet congratulated you
on regaining your title as Noble Consort.

86
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,430
I don't care about that at all.

87
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,800
When a man loves you,
he wants you to live well.

88
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,430
When he hates you, he wants you dead.

89
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:44,920
Men—

90
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,730
not a single one of them is any good.

91
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,800
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager specially
bestows upon Your Highnesses

92
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:03,660
the grape wine brought
by the envoys from Yan State.

93
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:07,970
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

94
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,860
This is so good.

95
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,320
I haven't had enough.

96
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:54,540
Noble Consort Yu,

97
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,960
this is a very precious wine
bestowed by Her Majesty.

98
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,960
Only one cup each.

99
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:58,910
You drank hers up...

100
00:08:58,910 --> 00:08:59,640
Why don't you

101
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,490
go complain to His Majesty?

102
00:09:06,110 --> 00:09:06,910
Ms. Tonghao,

103
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,120
I was ill a few days ago.

104
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:11,510
My stomach hasn't fully recovered,

105
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,110
so I really shouldn't drink.

106
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:18,210
Her Majesty was also very concerned

107
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,240
about Your Highness's vomiting last time.

108
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,630
She asked me to summon
the most experienced physician,

109
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,870
Physician Zhang,
from the Imperial Medical Bureau.

110
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,430
After the banquet ends,

111
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:28,690
I'll bring him to examine you again.

112
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:30,840
Your Highness Noble Consort Yu,

113
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,370
please return to your seat.

114
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,440
Mind the protocol.

115
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,510
Power-abusing wretch.

116
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,270
They say everyone from Yan State
is skilled at dancing.

117
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:15,730
Their reputation is indeed well-deserved.

118
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,500
Though they are stunning beauties,

119
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:22,480
they still can't compare to
Beautiful Lady Shanyi back then.

120
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,790
Indeed.

121
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:25,550
Bravo!

122
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,520
Truly, you're beauties

123
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:29,920
with exotic charm!

124
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,600
Mr. Wang,

125
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:34,480
the delegation from Yan State
has come from afar

126
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,270
to present dances
for His Majesty's birthday.

127
00:11:36,270 --> 00:11:37,730
Does the Ministry of Rites

128
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:39,800
have no reciprocal gift prepared?

129
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,790
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager,

130
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:47,510
the Imperial Music Bureau
has specially prepared a musical pageant

131
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,170
to present to the delegation.

132
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:52,120
A musical pageant?

133
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,720
Then what are we waiting for?

134
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:55,840
Begin.

135
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,360
Yes.

136
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:16,060
[Zhaluowahan, Emperor of Yan]

137
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,930
Zhaluowahan is the Emperor of Yan,

138
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:18,750
sinister and cunning behind his smile.

139
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,940
This is clearly mocking our country.

140
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:32,680
A man can be killed but not humiliated.

141
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,630
Even if we are at odds with our Emperor,

142
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:39,670
it's not for these Xia people
to mock us so casually.

143
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,300
Can't you see

144
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,380
they're trying to provoke us?

145
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,390
Bravo!

146
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,500
Excellent!

147
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,780
Your Majesty the Emperor,

148
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,930
we people of Yan love dancing!

149
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,880
May we join in?

150
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,100
Certainly!

151
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:14,240
Joy shared is joy doubled.

152
00:14:14,550 --> 00:14:16,070
I'll beat the drum for you myself!

153
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:17,470
Thank you, Your Majesty!

154
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,330
Keep the music playing!

155
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,680
Keep the dance going!

156
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,180
Your Highness,

157
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:54,030
you've already taken the medicine
that Physician Xiao prescribed.

158
00:14:54,030 --> 00:14:56,360
You must not take any other medicines now.

159
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:01,200
Physician Xiao's medicine won't
take effect for another three days.

160
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,730
But the Empress Dowager...

161
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:06,080
will send an imperial physician
the moment the banquet ends.

162
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,010
There's no time.

163
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:10,010
Your Highness, you mustn't!

164
00:15:10,010 --> 00:15:11,140
Physician Xiao said

165
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:14,150
all fast-acting medicines are
too harsh on the body.

166
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:16,130
If anything happens to you,

167
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,840
how am I supposed to go on living,

168
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:18,700
Your Highness?

169
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:22,230
Then I'll only take one pill.

170
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:25,100
If it's not effective enough,

171
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:26,960
I'll take the other two.

172
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,840
Go find Physician Xiao immediately

173
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,640
and ask him how to counteract it.

174
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:57,320
Where is Consort Xie?

175
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,200
She just left.

176
00:15:58,560 --> 00:15:59,960
She looked unsteady on her feet

177
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,720
and pale.

178
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,040
Her maid wasn't with her either.

179
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:04,670
What?

180
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,130
Their dancing isn't that impressive.

181
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:16,200
Let's split up and search.

182
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,270
But Your Highness, you...

183
00:16:17,270 --> 00:16:18,120
What's there to fear?

184
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,550
Nothing will happen to me.

185
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,240
Finding Xie Yong'er is what matters now.

186
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:23,500
I'm afraid something will happen to her.

187
00:16:51,210 --> 00:16:51,920
Lord Cao,

188
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:53,670
let me toast to you.

189
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:54,890
To you!

190
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:58,900
Sorry.

191
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:01,360
Pardon me.

192
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,560
Where's my jade pendant?

193
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:16,230
Where is the jade pendant
I wear at my waist?

194
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,440
If you suspect him,

195
00:17:24,829 --> 00:17:25,790
just search him.

196
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:59,000
The jade pendant really is on him!

197
00:17:59,220 --> 00:18:00,020
Quickly check

198
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:02,200
if we still have our jade pendants!

199
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:05,550
How strange.

200
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,720
How did the pendant

201
00:18:08,770 --> 00:18:10,960
I wear at my waist end up with this envoy?

202
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:13,090
Could it be that you stole it when no one

203
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:14,580
was looking...

204
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:16,610
I...

205
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,270
I didn't!

206
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,230
You're framing me!

207
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,680
Let go of me...

208
00:18:23,690 --> 00:18:24,960
Your Majesty the Emperor,

209
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:25,690
we are people

210
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,020
from a humble land.

211
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,600
We've never seen such splendor before.

212
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:32,680
Perhaps greed momentarily overcame him.

213
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,920
We beg Your Majesty's forgiveness.

214
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,040
Your Majesty,

215
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:45,050
you must uphold justice for this subject.

216
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:47,630
Your Majesty,

217
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,490
this person

218
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:50,960
is yours to deal with as you see fit.

219
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,170
Alright, alright!

220
00:19:03,590 --> 00:19:05,710
It's just a jade pendant.

221
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,810
Why make such a fuss?

222
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:12,640
Since the envoy likes it,

223
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:15,080
just gift it to him.

224
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:17,690
Don't let a small jade pendant

225
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:21,010
damage the friendship
between our two nations.

226
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:24,350
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager is
absolutely right.

227
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:26,240
I was inconsiderate.

228
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:41,880
Mr. Wang.

229
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:45,110
Where exactly

230
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,820
did you find the pendant just now?

231
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,090
Inside his robe.

232
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:50,950
Where specifically?

233
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,200
Where specifically?

234
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:54,830
The place...

235
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,680
Around his chest.

236
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:01,110
From what I see,
the Yan delegation's clothing

237
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:03,110
is designed differently from ours.

238
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,200
Such a small object,

239
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:07,080
placed inside the robe,

240
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:09,980
would actually remain
near the chest...

241
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,510
How interesting.

242
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:13,970
Mr. Wang,

243
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,200
try it.

244
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:20,250
Well...

245
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:21,810
Uh...

246
00:20:23,510 --> 00:20:24,070
Uh...

247
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,160
No,

248
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:38,790
that's not how it was just now!

249
00:20:38,790 --> 00:20:40,070
It was clearly at his chest just now!

250
00:20:40,070 --> 00:20:41,090
How did it suddenly...

251
00:20:41,090 --> 00:20:41,890
Well... um...

252
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,810
No, it wasn't like that just now!

253
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:45,670
No, it wasn't like that. No, no...

254
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:52,240
Mr. Wang, there seems to be

255
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:55,330
something unusual about your sleeve.

256
00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:57,390
I wouldn't want to wrong you.

257
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,450
Quickly,

258
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,510
show it to everyone

259
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,600
to prove your innocence.

260
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:03,420
Your Maj...

261
00:21:07,790 --> 00:21:08,270
Your...

262
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:14,840
Just now,

263
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:16,500
I drank too much,

264
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:18,370
so my mind was unclear.

265
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,310
Please spare me, Your Majesty.

266
00:21:20,310 --> 00:21:21,510
Please spare my life!

267
00:21:21,510 --> 00:21:22,340
Please!

268
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:23,240
Fine.

269
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,270
Take Mr. Wang away

270
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:28,500
and help him sober up.

271
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,160
Your Majesty! Your...

272
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,190
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

273
00:21:32,190 --> 00:21:33,350
Please spare me, Your Majesty!

274
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:34,950
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

275
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,510
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager!

276
00:21:36,510 --> 00:21:38,110
Empress Dowager, please save me!

277
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:39,110
Empress Dowager!

278
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:41,440
Empress Dowager, save me!

279
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:45,030
Your Majesty is wise.

280
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:48,590
It was all just a misunderstanding.

281
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:49,190
Be seated.

282
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,670
Thank you, Your Majesty!

283
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:03,690
Mother,

284
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,920
allow me to toast you.

285
00:22:09,070 --> 00:22:10,220
You displayed

286
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:12,560
quite the authority today.

287
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,770
Mother, you flatter me.

288
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,240
You don't

289
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:24,000
need me anymore.

290
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:33,880
My son,

291
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:38,510
you can host
the birthday banquet yourself now.

292
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:56,650
Where is she?

293
00:22:58,110 --> 00:22:59,910
Where on earth did she run off to?

294
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:15,890
Yong'er,

295
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:17,550
are you all right?

296
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,010
I'm fine.

297
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:22,200
This is...

298
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:26,100
Don't look.

299
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:26,930
Don't look.

300
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:28,500
I'm begging you.

301
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:29,360
Go now.

302
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:30,630
Just leave me.

303
00:23:34,420 --> 00:23:36,240
You need to go back
and change your clothes.

304
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,370
Can you still stand?

305
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,110
I can't stand up.

306
00:23:42,350 --> 00:23:42,810
Come on,

307
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,300
I'll carry you.

308
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:09,880
Why is it you?

309
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:10,700
Stop talking.

310
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,050
Save your strength.

311
00:24:12,410 --> 00:24:13,810
I'm going to stand up now.

312
00:24:37,590 --> 00:24:38,450
Your Highness,

313
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,320
it's exactly as you predicted.

314
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:45,790
Proceed to Kunyu Palace!

315
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,700
Where is everyone?

316
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,540
Help!

317
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,400
Maids!

318
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,700
Where is everyone?

319
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:11,120
Where is everyone? Where did you all go?

320
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:13,120
Yong'er!

321
00:25:13,790 --> 00:25:14,680
Where is everyone?

322
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,810
Where did you all go?

323
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:19,320
Who dares make such noise here?

324
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,160
How improper!

325
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,750
Aren't those Consort Xie

326
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:32,790
and Noble Consort Yu, who left

327
00:25:31,130 --> 00:25:34,990
[Kunyu Palace]

328
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,500
the banquet early?

329
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:39,070
I've been waiting here for you two
for quite some time.

330
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:43,810
I happened to encounter Consort Xie
outside the hall just now.

331
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:45,460
Seeing she was unwell,

332
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:47,130
I brought her back.

333
00:25:47,250 --> 00:25:50,020
[Kunyu Palace]

334
00:25:47,930 --> 00:25:50,070
There're so many servants in the palace,

335
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:52,560
and yet you, a noble consort,

336
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,510
had to carry her back?

337
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:57,200
Enough.

338
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,480
You two,

339
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:01,790
stop trying to deceive me.

340
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:03,770
Tonghao,

341
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:05,070
go and see

342
00:26:05,550 --> 00:26:06,960
what they're up to!

343
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

344
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,440
Your Majesty,

345
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:26,430
there are bloodstains on

346
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:28,240
Her Highness Consort Xie's skirt.

347
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:29,380
Bloodstains?

348
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:30,520
Consort Xie,

349
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,060
what happened?

350
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:33,680
I...

351
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:36,510
Perhaps her time of the month came early.

352
00:26:36,510 --> 00:26:37,510
It soiled her hem.

353
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,510
I feared it would be improper,

354
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,530
so I

355
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,080
brought her back alone.

356
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,560
Consort Xie?

357
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:46,400
Consort Xie!

358
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:48,350
Lift your head and look at me!

359
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,420
Is that truly the case?

360
00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:56,040
Your Majesty...

361
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:57,440
I...

362
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:03,330
Yong'er?

363
00:27:03,850 --> 00:27:04,380
Yong'er?

364
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:05,370
Xie Yong'er!

365
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,410
Xie Yong'er?

366
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,110
Your Majesty,

367
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:17,510
Her Highness Consort Xie has awakened.

368
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:18,830
How is Consort Xie?

369
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,560
Her Highness has deficient kidney qi.

370
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:23,760
Her pulse is weak and unstable.

371
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:26,030
And she experienced massive bleeding.

372
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:27,090
It appears to be...

373
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,860
a miscarriage.

374
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,820
A miscarriage?

375
00:27:30,110 --> 00:27:30,510
Quick,

376
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:32,010
go inform the Emperor!

377
00:27:32,070 --> 00:27:32,400
Yes.

378
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:34,480
Wait!

379
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:37,640
Didn't an imperial physician say before

380
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,550
that Consort Xie was not pregnant?

381
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:40,000
Yes,

382
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,000
Physician Xiao did say so.

383
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:44,260
Well...

384
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:45,590
Perhaps

385
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,070
the pregnancy was too early,

386
00:27:48,070 --> 00:27:49,670
so her pulse was not obvious.

387
00:27:50,060 --> 00:27:52,330
This subject only inferred it

388
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:54,280
from her other symptoms.

389
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,660
What symptoms?

390
00:27:57,590 --> 00:27:58,990
Her Highness Consort Xie

391
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:01,520
appears to have taken...

392
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,410
an abortifacient.

393
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,980
An abortifacient?

394
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:09,750
Leave.

395
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:11,440
Yes.

396
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,200
Consort Xie,

397
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:25,730
you have quite the audacity!

398
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:28,280
The Emperor has few heirs.

399
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:30,420
We finally had hope of having a prince,

400
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:33,170
and you dared to
commit such an outrageous act!

401
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,260
I didn't take any abortifacient!

402
00:28:35,410 --> 00:28:38,070
Please investigate thoroughly,
Your Majesty!

403
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,310
Your Majesty,

404
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:41,140
I was hoping

405
00:28:41,510 --> 00:28:43,110
to give you another grandson

406
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:45,310
to keep the little prince company.

407
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:47,840
How could I possibly
take any abortifacient?

408
00:28:48,090 --> 00:28:49,190
Oh, Your Majesty,

409
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,220
perhaps it was because

410
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:53,520
I vomited in public,

411
00:28:54,270 --> 00:28:56,340
making people think I was pregnant.

412
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,040
Someone became jealous,

413
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,830
so...

414
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:01,590
You mean

415
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,960
you were drugged.

416
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:16,640
Tell me,

417
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:19,520
who drugged you?

418
00:29:21,890 --> 00:29:23,160
I don't know.

419
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,040
Is it that you don't know,

420
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,640
or that you dare not say?

421
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,140
Tell me!

422
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,110
Why are you looking at me?

423
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:49,790
Noble Consort Yu?

424
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,130
It seems this matter

425
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,690
has everything to do with you.

426
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,640
How could it possibly be me?

427
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,770
If not you, then who?

428
00:29:57,590 --> 00:30:00,310
You previously sent someone
to assassinate Consort Shu,

429
00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:02,720
and now you've drugged Consort Xie!

430
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:06,000
You'll stop at nothing
to win the Emperor's favor!

431
00:30:06,310 --> 00:30:08,910
All my son's affection for you
has been wasted!

432
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:09,620
Guards!

433
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:10,410
-Yes!
-Yes!

434
00:30:10,410 --> 00:30:12,010
Seize this demonic consort!

435
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:13,340
It wasn't me!

436
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:14,940
Say something!

437
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:19,470
Why is Your Majesty so certain it was me?

438
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,010
If I really did drug her,

439
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:22,570
why would I bring her back?

440
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:24,400
Wouldn't it be better to leave her there?

441
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:26,550
You were just trying to cover your tracks!

442
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:28,160
I just came out of the Cold Palace.

443
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:30,400
How could I have had the chance
to drug her?

444
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:32,730
Perhaps the real culprit is someone else!

445
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,880
Say something!

446
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:44,670
My stomach hurts so much.

447
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:51,850
I haven't eaten anything today.

448
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,680
Like Consort Xie,

449
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:56,680
I also only drank the cup of wine
that Ms. Tonghao brought.

450
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:58,490
Why is my stomach cramping too?

451
00:31:00,570 --> 00:31:01,450
Your Majesty,

452
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:02,510
please

453
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,310
seek justice for Consort Xie and me!

454
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,070
Your Highness!

455
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:06,190
Your Highness!

456
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,440
You cannot wrongly accuse this lowly maid!

457
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:10,000
Your Majesty, please be fair!

458
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:12,290
This maid did nothing!

459
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:14,160
This maid would never dare!

460
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:17,180
This maid would never dare!

461
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:26,040
Your Highness, are you alright?

462
00:31:26,890 --> 00:31:27,820
It hurts so much!

463
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:31,260
Your Highness, please slow down.

464
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:35,740
Your Highness,

465
00:31:36,030 --> 00:31:37,690
the Empress Dowager has left.

466
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,110
Turn around.

467
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:42,240
Let's go settle this with Xie Yong'er.

468
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,100
Your Highness,

469
00:31:59,330 --> 00:32:00,590
the medicine is ready.

470
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:01,650
Please take it.

471
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:08,030
The medicine was prepared
by Physician Xiao.

472
00:32:08,030 --> 00:32:08,890
It's very safe.

473
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:17,310
Has the fetus been taken care of?

474
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,670
I found a tree far away

475
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:21,260
and buried it there...

476
00:32:21,260 --> 00:32:22,060
Don't tell me.

477
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,540
Your Highness.

478
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,480
Do you know, Ling?

479
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:48,270
I used to think I was the chosen one,

480
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,630
and that with the script in hand,

481
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:54,610
I could change the course
and everything myself.

482
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:58,610
But in the end, I couldn't do anything.

483
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:04,270
I couldn't even protect my own child.

484
00:33:07,270 --> 00:33:08,560
I've failed myself.

485
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,280
I've failed him too.

486
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:14,570
No, Your Highness. Don't think that way.

487
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,880
There are many people you've failed,

488
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,210
but he's not one of them.

489
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:19,550
Please calm down, Your Highness.

490
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:20,720
Her Highness Consort Xie is ill...

491
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,000
Chu Qi, take Ling out.

492
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:22,310
Yes.

493
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,320
Let's go.

494
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:31,480
You also suspect
Prince Duan is full of lies, don't you?

495
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:34,280
Otherwise, why do you keep
making excuses for him?

496
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,050
What about Prince Duan?

497
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,430
I know everything about you two.

498
00:33:39,430 --> 00:33:41,630
How long are you going to keep hiding it?

499
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,160
I don't know what you're talking about.

500
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:45,970
You were almost dead.

501
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:48,330
Are you still going to deceive yourself?

502
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,110
Let me ask you:

503
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,310
the new Commander of the Imperial Guards,

504
00:33:56,310 --> 00:33:57,110
Zhao Wucheng—

505
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,100
whose man is he?

506
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:03,030
Even the Imperial Guards
protecting the entire Imperial City

507
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:04,890
are under Prince Duan's command.

508
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:05,960
How could he fail to protect

509
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:07,360
your small Kunyu Palace?

510
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:10,400
Was he truly powerless,
or did he do it deliberately?

511
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:12,600
Don't you know the answer in your heart?

512
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:17,570
He keeps saying he loves you
and will protect you.

513
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,110
But when you were carrying his child,

514
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:20,800
he gave you no protection at all.

515
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,030
If that wasn't using you as bait

516
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,480
to divert the Empress Dowager,

517
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,409
then what was it?

518
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:33,480
If you don't believe

519
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:35,810
that Yu Wanyin would say such things
to Xie Yong'er,

520
00:34:35,810 --> 00:34:36,540
that's fine.

521
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,020
Let me ask you as someone else.

522
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:46,679
How...

523
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,000
are...

524
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:50,469
you? [spoken in English]

525
00:34:51,630 --> 00:34:52,230
Answer me!

526
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,989
How are you? [spoken in English]

527
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:03,570
Zhang San's Diary.

528
00:35:03,670 --> 00:35:05,150
I've caused you all to be punished.

529
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:07,030
I feel terrible about it.

530
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:08,670
Today,

531
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:11,550
I've specially invited you all here,

532
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,810
hoping these pastries

533
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,520
might make amends.

534
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:25,720
Crown Prince,

535
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,320
what's the meaning of this?

536
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,920
This is rotten swill for pigs!

537
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,380
Do you take us for beggars?

538
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,610
This is impossible.

539
00:35:40,230 --> 00:35:40,840
I didn't!

540
00:35:46,550 --> 00:35:47,150
Come here!

541
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:49,160
They were perfectly good pastries
just moments ago!

542
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:51,070
How did they become rotten scraps?

543
00:35:51,070 --> 00:35:53,000
I watched them being put in myself!

544
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:53,630
Speak!

545
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:56,050
Please calm down, Your Highness!

546
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:57,550
This servant did follow

547
00:35:57,550 --> 00:35:59,110
Your Highness's instructions.

548
00:35:59,110 --> 00:35:59,980
You're lying!

549
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:02,220
Who put you up to framing me?

550
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,000
Tell me!

551
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,800
Please calm down, Crown Prince.

552
00:36:04,800 --> 00:36:06,960
This eunuch's offense
doesn't warrant death.

553
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,820
Please show mercy, Crown Prince.

554
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:21,970
So it was him.

555
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,560
Since this is your kind gesture,

556
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:36,630
I shall

557
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:38,360
accept it

558
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:39,590
on behalf of all the other princes.
